<body>
    <h1>T5 -Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"c001a5b79832" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduc=
tion">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"4b2a9b27ce3f" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.1 Pu=
rpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f51389246b14">This document provides a comprehensive technic=
al overview of the 3-tier serverless architecture deployed on Amazon Web Se=
rvices (AWS). The system consists of a React frontend hosted on Amazon S3, =
a Node.js Express backend deployed via AWS Lambda using the Serverless Fram=
ework, and a MySQL database hosted on Amazon RDS. Deployment automation is =
implemented using GitHub Actions.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8b7d785c5b8d">This document aims to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2368a77ecb14">
<li local-id=3D"da199717e6fe">
<p local-id=3D"2bee796ede36">Explain the architecture and infrastructure</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"c84aaab3068d">
<p local-id=3D"1b33f842acd4">Document the CI/CD automation process</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"456bed3f5e58">
<p local-id=3D"bdc2c2242df8">Describe security, monitoring, and cost consid=
erations</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"547f7d408e94">
<p local-id=3D"c7b8c633adad">Provide implementation transparency</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"9be0e2cbee9d" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-IntendedAudience">=
Intended Audience</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"13a8063ca3ba">
<li local-id=3D"116022e9f9ae">
<p local-id=3D"146d7d871be5">Chief Technology Officers (CTO)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"42f71907babf">
<p local-id=3D"acfb9826c022">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13188f6d67ee">
<p local-id=3D"015eb814cec1">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9ec50c11d7ca">
<p local-id=3D"6fa5ebb29dec">Developers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3f3aa947ac34">
<p local-id=3D"8a9d7bd33840">Technical Resellers</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d78f4b583b12">
<h2 local-id=3D"e55829f6f400" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 Scop=
e</h2>
<p local-id=3D"288903ed2fc7">This document covers:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8c1ce440ab8f">
<li local-id=3D"9d2f190f805e">
<p local-id=3D"1a3cf12a8a60">Static frontend hosting using Amazon S3</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"4b8fb9e11ba2">
<p local-id=3D"270d9ed887eb">Backend API deployment using AWS Lambda</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"1bf0243b0704">
<p local-id=3D"b67dcfc8d3ba">Database hosting using Amazon RDS (MySQL)</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"f47776bdf3ae">
<p local-id=3D"fe206ec1408e">CI/CD automation using GitHub Actions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af1476f9b63e">
<p local-id=3D"739f27d7ff22">Security and configuration setup</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d0dc96b84cea">Out of Scope:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cb610db16cbd">
<li local-id=3D"5f318d2466e2">
<p local-id=3D"21b8c806df3b">Multi-region deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92bb8c6305bd">
<p local-id=3D"bc78f99496d1">Infrastructure as Code (Terraform)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6a177b924287">
<p local-id=3D"57dfb07ec59e">Automated testing frameworks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c208f6af047d">
<p local-id=3D"7d80631df9ef">Advanced monitoring and alerting</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"457a89a6d10a">
<h1 local-id=3D"a1413c5ab107" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDevOps=
Project">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"6c112fb4e58c" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition">2.1=
 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"630d3412a18e">DevOps integrates development and operations p=
ractices to enable automated, reliable, and scalable software delivery. In =
this implementation, DevOps principles were applied to deploy a serverless =
3-tier architecture with automated CI/CD.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"93a4bb5336f3"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260225-174510.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"170f93b785360e60b09e5869c6572d7c22d19bbbf0=
