iner-id=3D"1797783574" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-me=
dia-id=3D"b1ca39b5-a671-491a-aef3-d32749f4ad8d" data-media-type=3D"file" he=
ight=3D"141"></span>
<p local-id=3D"bf659518cdc0"></p>
<p local-id=3D"dba9e943af72"><strong>Description:</strong> This screenshot =
confirms that the CI/CD workflow executed successfully, validating automate=
d backend and frontend deployment.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"3f2a56b99b9e">
<h2 local-id=3D"57533c519490" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-2.2KeyPrinciples=
=E2=80=93AWSWell-ArchitectedFramework">2.2 Key Principles =E2=80=93 AWS Wel=
l-Architected Framework</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"b91760258407" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-OperationalExcelle=
nce">Operational Excellence</h3>
<p local-id=3D"9eba5a7aeb87">Automated CI/CD using GitHub Actions and struc=
tured serverless deployment.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"e6a6d906930e" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-Security">Security=
</h3>
<p local-id=3D"bcc05dd7740a">IAM roles, VPC-based Lambda connectivity, and =
restricted database access.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"4e95fa163b4e" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-Reliability">Relia=
bility</h3>
<p local-id=3D"d124ec5a21dc">Managed services (Lambda, RDS, API Gateway) en=
sure high availability.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"dabc1a2873c9" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-PerformanceEfficie=
ncy">Performance Efficiency</h3>
<p local-id=3D"29ad4ac513db">Serverless compute and lightweight database in=
stance selection.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"7dfac69cf98e" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-CostOptimization">=
Cost Optimization</h3>
<p local-id=3D"81e2ebc7d78a">Pay-per-use Lambda model and right-sized RDS i=
nstance.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"5ad77bb31c0b" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-Sustainability">Su=
stainability</h3>
<p local-id=3D"131de919ed2d">Serverless architecture reduces idle compute c=
onsumption.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"0ccd527f74b6">
<h2 local-id=3D"475f81319bbf" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObjecti=
ves">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"ab18f7497093">
<li local-id=3D"ae20a23b184a">
<p local-id=3D"d365be52a9b4">Deploy a functional 3-tier architecture</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"ca099b0f5fa6">
<p local-id=3D"c496f6315dfe">Automate deployment pipeline</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfae6394b2b5">
<p local-id=3D"5cb758e56044">Secure backend-database communication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f70e3cdafd61">
<p local-id=3D"d012a180e4e4">Validate end-to-end connectivity</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e67889dfc621">
<h2 local-id=3D"82c6269a4a37" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-2.4ConstraintsandA=
ssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3760984392b6">Constraints:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"737c139f8bb4">
<li local-id=3D"3ce0f8a0bc8c">
<p local-id=3D"810af5283ce9">Single region (ap-south-1)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7076d4d30f38">
<p local-id=3D"f28ad3016d4f">Limited project duration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f6d2636aa2b">
<p local-id=3D"026cb881f9c7">Budget-aware infrastructure sizing</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"821f3c6bbd92">Assumptions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ab3cfde5fe18">
<li local-id=3D"c83c98969fca">
<p local-id=3D"f80ecd239a2f">Moderate traffic</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c07e3f6cbf76">
<p local-id=3D"6a47833e2e5e">Single development environment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfa55faf194b">
<p local-id=3D"062c42aac076">Manual validation acceptable</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0b0d8a76b432">
<h1 local-id=3D"d15ad225fc88" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-3.ArchitectureandI=
nfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"2ca94b0d63a8" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-AWSArchitectureDia=
gram">AWS Architecture Diagram</h3><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-=
wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D=
"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"f4ca9514-583a-483d-8cf2-879=
c07c3a43c-20260304-193924.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"47e0ff=
c5814d0aedef8c691de7bc9940f7a4159cf0776fe20961e3163ae88360" data-image-src=
