<p local-id=3D"191cc20d5e5a"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"86d8b4871928" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-3.1InfrastructureO=
verview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4588838e3d1c">The system follows a 3-tier serverless model:<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"0949acc0727a">User<br>
=E2=86=93<br>
S3 (Frontend)<br>
=E2=86=93<br>
API Gateway<br>
=E2=86=93<br>
Lambda (Backend)<br>
=E2=86=93<br>
RDS (Database)</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-cen=
ter-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embed=
ded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260225-185443.png" width=3D"468" loa=
ding=3D"lazy" src=3D"afa6f9434904625dddde9b56556115f1d44f4f00c285733ed5bbfe=
aa1b10c8ab" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/at=
tachments/1797783574/image-20260225-185443.png?version=3D2&amp;modification=
Date=3D1772045691194&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"468"=
 data-width=3D"5930" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resour=
ce-id=3D"1805582337" data-linked-resource-version=3D"2" data-linked-resourc=
e-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260225-=
185443.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked=
-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1=
797783574" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"1f=
f06a64-84c8-47ee-a5a5-7431a84f0117" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"36">=
</span>
<p local-id=3D"b5bfbb0583e0">This diagram shows the core request flow of th=
e 3-tier serverless application. The user accesses the React frontend hoste=
d on Amazon S3, which sends API requests to Amazon API Gateway. API Gateway=
 invokes the AWS Lambda backend, which retrieves data from the Amazon RDS M=
ySQL database. The response is returned through the same path and displayed=
 to the user.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-cent=
er-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedd=
ed-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260225-184459.png" width=3D"468" load=
ing=3D"lazy" src=3D"88cc0a4e445f514d23f204b8339c155a316660dd6933a67636a4f69=
880bea50f" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/att=
achments/1797783574/image-20260225-184459.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationD=
ate=3D1772045106209&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1257"=
 data-width=3D"2209" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resour=
ce-id=3D"1805221890" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resourc=
e-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260225-=
184459.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked=
-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1=
797783574" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"c3=
a1b02c-2dc0-4db9-aa64-186f76a8d69c" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"266"=
></span>
<p local-id=3D"77850a094879">This diagram provides a detailed view of runti=
me flow, database interaction, security controls, and CI/CD automation.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cd09b4ecd06f">
<li local-id=3D"3297061df07a">
<p local-id=3D"62d53075ec45">The vertical flow represents the user request =
lifecycle from browser to frontend (S3), API Gateway, Lambda, and back to t=
he user.</p></li>
</ul>
<ul local-id=3D"123654c1e48e">
<li local-id=3D"f596da414c2d">
<p local-id=3D"4316e4f18830">The horizontal branch shows Lambda communicati=
ng with Amazon RDS (MySQL database <code>testdb</code>, table <code>tutoria=
ls</code>) to execute SQL queries and retrieve data.</p></li>
</ul>
<ul local-id=3D"19f654edbe85">
<li local-id=3D"f45a3d7a752c">
<p local-id=3D"375edbfb4d93">The upward arrows represent the response path:=
 RDS =E2=86=92 Lambda =E2=86=92 API Gateway =E2=86=92 S3 =E2=86=92 User int=
erface update.</p></li>
</ul>
<ul local-id=3D"331b43fedd38">
<li local-id=3D"0e14a5578608">
<p local-id=3D"14df461b47c2">The Security panel highlights key controls:</p=
></li>
</ul>
<ul local-id=3D"dbaa295e55d7">
<li local-id=3D"45fc18e067de">
<p local-id=3D"710730771cfa">Lambda attached to VPC</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d813adea12f">
<p local-id=3D"dcb9b7072b05">RDS protected by Security Group</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f6fbdaa6664">
<p local-id=3D"fe549e71d7cc">Only Lambda Security Group allowed inbound</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"7074ea5d4bb9">
<p local-id=3D"e8529564a3b8">IAM Execution Role attached to Lambda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3dd435bd6da6">
<p local-id=3D"319205548bf4">S3 bucket configured as public read-only</p></=
li>
</ul>
<ul local-id=3D"33bdd872c647">
<li local-id=3D"2e03c994b679">
<p local-id=3D"312e25c0c4d8">The CI/CD panel demonstrates automation:</p></=
li>
</ul>
<ul local-id=3D"7570b95a84eb">
<li local-id=3D"550488ad0dcd">
<p local-id=3D"b854b04a72a6">Push to main branch triggers GitHub Actions</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc33a4744570">
<p local-id=3D"18fd9d0e9a5b">Backend deployed using <code>serverless deploy=
</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc37a77d6f70">
<p local-id=3D"976d7810dc65">Frontend built and uploaded to S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef39c10713d4">
<p local-id=3D"ad912275d4c3">Lambda automatically updated</p></li>
</ul>
<ul local-id=3D"14181ec21556">
<li local-id=3D"036b23864100">
<p local-id=3D"ce24ac5ea3f4">The diagram clearly separates:</p></li>
</ul>
<ul local-id=3D"f55f313f8e3a">
<li local-id=3D"c2064b2941ee">
<p local-id=3D"39256a0e8f86">Presentation layer (S3 React frontend)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"e0b427cca674">
<p local-id=3D"0a37aff90799">Application layer (Lambda backend)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"898b042d3556">
<p local-id=3D"ae882cc24acf">Data layer (RDS MySQL)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7e222a3114d4">
<p local-id=3D"f717a8212033">Automation layer (GitHub Actions)</p></li>
</ul>
