<hr local-id=3D"0887084c8c34">
<h1 local-id=3D"c860172cae40" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-7.Security&amp;Com=
pliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c137642dbd6f">Security controls implemented:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"580b4529db96">
<li local-id=3D"4489cce3d5b5">
<p local-id=3D"da10dad7d04d">IAM least privilege</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ac6a7a8ed20">
<p local-id=3D"926bf126f99d">Security group restrictions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1a4151974384">
<p local-id=3D"46d0dce29cd9">Public read-only S3 bucket policy</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eea682ec352f">
<p local-id=3D"1350f06f0b10">No hardcoded credentials</p></li>
</ul>
