<p local-id=3D"c9cb97c6847b">Phase 1: Backend and Database Setup (2 Hours)<=
br>
Phase 2: Frontend Deployment (2 Hours)<br>
Phase 3: CI/CD Automation &amp; Validation (2 Hours)</p>
<p local-id=3D"5bbbbcd4af25">Final Delivery: Completed within 6-hour timeli=
ne.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b65014bebcd1">
<h1 local-id=3D"cd476a449338" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-11.ContinuousImpro=
vement">11. Continuous Improvement</h1>
<p local-id=3D"8819648fd9bf">Future enhancements:</p>
