<hr local-id=3D"72f3172ec262">
<h1 local-id=3D"f7de574ee5b7" id=3D"T5-TechnicalDocument-12.Conclusion">12.=
 Conclusion</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e0c12386fcbf">This project successfully implemented a 3-tier=
 serverless architecture with CI/CD automation using AWS and GitHub Actions=
. The solution demonstrates automation, cloud-native design, and cost-aware=
 infrastructure deployment.</p>
